      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ANALYZATION (1) ran right away with it after leading to make it two in a row at this track over 500m (28.15). Winner at his latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. In top form and looks a key chance again. PAW RAYNOR (8) was strongly fancied latest and proved too good with a 4 length win at this track in a handy 27.97. Outside box to overcome but in form and has the ability. Ran the fastest time on the program in his latest win. Can measure up again. BABY BEETS (4) is in sizzling form lately, rocketing around Ballarat in 25.19 to score two back then following on with a 28.24 win over 500m at this track. Recent form strong for this and rates a key player again. DEEP THINKER (2) placed last time (28.25) at this track in a Grade 5 H, finishing second and beaten 4 lengths. Has already won out of this draw.",
